ofits and more whose commitment and investment make this conference Virginia s premier environmental conference  We greatly appreciate their support  To thank them for their involvement and investment  we have dedicated this  Partners  section of our site to advertise those who have made a financial commitment to the conference as a host  sponsoring organization  conference sponsor or exhibitor  Additionally  they are advertised in our program and a conference exhibit hall map referencing the locations of those organizations is located where is always included in our conference program  Please visit our  partner with us  section to review the options available  Be a part of making this year s conference great while marketing to this audience of more than 600 top environmental professionals from across the state  You may also download a copy of those opportunities here  Exhibitors and Sponsors Information    VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 